No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado.

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $114,817.19 for the period October 19, 1996, through September 9, 1997, to be paid equally by Kansas and Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 803.]
